data.description: Charming and cozy, this delightful 3 bedroom, 1 bath home in Kimberly, Idaho is perfect for those seeking a comfortable and affordable living space. With 1,064 square feet of well-designed layout, this property offers a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living area creates an excellent space for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with family. The three bedrooms provide comfortable accommodations, and the well-appointed bathroom ensures convenience. Additionally, the home boasts a lovely backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. Don't miss the opportunity to own this charming residence, ideal for first-time homebuyers or those looking to downsize without sacrificing comfort and style.
